**2. `tests/e2e/cross-feature-integration.spec.ts`** (~400 lines)
- **Purpose:** Test interactions between different features (tasks + calendar + time tracking + automation)
- **Key Tests:**
  - Create recurring task → view on calendar → start timer → verify time entry
  - Create automation rule → trigger condition → verify action executes
  - Create note with wikilink → click link → verify graph updates → navigate
  - Add custom field to task → export CSV → verify field included
  - Task with dependencies → mark blocker complete → verify unblocked
- **Dependencies:** All stores, automation engine
- **Integration:** Most complex test suite (cross-cutting concerns)

**3. `tests/e2e/backup-restore.spec.ts`** (~250 lines)
- **Purpose:** Test data integrity through backup/restore cycle
- **Key Tests:**
  - Full backup → clear DB → restore → verify 100% data restoration
  - Edge cases: empty notes, nested subtasks, recurring events with instances
  - Schema migration simulation (v2.0 → v2.1)
  - Large dataset (1000+ items) backup/restore performance
- **Dependencies:** brainBackup service, all stores
- **Integration:** Critical data safety net

**4. `tests/e2e/automation-engine.spec.ts`** (~200 lines)
- **Purpose:** Test automation rule creation, execution, and edge cases
- **Key Tests:**
  - "When task → Done, create new task" rule execution
  - Loop prevention (task A creates B, B creates A → max depth 10)
  - Multiple rules on same trigger → verify ordered execution
  - Background execution via Service Worker
- **Dependencies:** automationEngine service, Service Worker
- **Integration:** New complex feature (high risk)

**5. `tests/e2e/recurring-tasks-events.spec.ts`** (~200 lines)
- **Purpose:** Test recurring pattern generation and instance management
- **Key Tests:**
  - Daily recurring task → verify 30-day instances generated
  - Weekly recurring (Mon/Wed) → verify correct day filtering
