## Implementation Notes

### Decisions Made
- [2025-01-28] - Use Playwright over Cypress because already configured, better TypeScript support
- [2025-01-28] - Pareto analysis: Focus on 5 test suites (88% bug coverage) vs. 20+ suites (95% coverage but 10x time)
